name: QuickTax 2009 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .Q09 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: Intuit Canada changed the name of QuickTax to TurboTax in 2011. TurboTax is also the name used by Intuit's U.S. tax return software.

description: Tax return created by QuickTax 2009, a program that assists in filing Canadian tax returns for the 2009 tax year; stores Canadian tax forms and data filled out by the user; used in the 2010 calendar year to file taxes for the previous 2009 tax year.
